===Noun===
'''secant''' (''plural'' '''secants''')

#{{geometry}} A [[straight]] [[line]] that [[intersect]]s a [[curve]] at two or more [[point]]s.
#{{trigonometry}} In a [[right triangle]], the [[reciprocal]] of the [[cosine]] of an [[angle]]. Symbol: [[sec]]

